{"tid":2097090,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"哈利波特香港版","createTime":"2020-07-06T14:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T19:28:48.000Z","uid":69866,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d03b087ed0263506663465c4afd01273b19b6abd","tid":2097090,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oDDYRPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoDDYRPL.jpg&h=73d4dbb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n.<br />\n,,<br />\n,,<br />\n..<br />\n..<br />\n,,<br />\n..<br />\n,,.<br />\n..<br />\n,,<br />\n...<br />\n,,,,<br />\n....<br />\n,<br />\n,,,.<br />\n.,<br />\n.,,.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wZOqwPZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwZOqwPZ.jpg&h=36b36921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去去武器走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6wPpNoW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wPpNoW.jpg&h=5f3e4a40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疾疾護法現身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1tqwQ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1tqwQ8.jpg&h=c43af049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麻瓜，仲想走？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPHyFLr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPHyFLr.jpg&h=700a0417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n預言家日報訪問麻瓜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjmfT6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjmfT6p.jpg&h=f73c9ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLumus Solem<br />\n使魔杖發出太陽一般的強光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1TqwUj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1TqwUj.jpg&h=422c79c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nImmobulus<br />\n使被施咒的全部目標定住不動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uz7SbUL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuz7SbUL.jpg&h=a9d1102a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBrackium Emendo<br />\n哈洛特試圖修復哈利骨折的胳膊時所用的咒語。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/udUJiAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FudUJiAA.jpg&h=642b4fc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAguamenti<br />\n召喚水源的咒語。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGGGPHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGGGPHM.jpg&h=2b42e78f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRepello muggletum，Muffliato<br />\n防止麻瓜靠近的咒語。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNgzqgR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNgzqgR.jpg&h=76b5a8b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDissendium<br />\n使物體左右分離的咒語。"},{"pid":"ad8f0b9167ea10d1f8794ce3af3a96da871536a8","tid":2097090,"uid":55080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"睇到好尷尬..."},{"pid":"b1a0f3df6874276655c46d398f8a25b697c448e2","tid":2097090,"uid":219398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:38:08.000Z","msg":".."},{"pid":"4b98a911857a6321dea08131821158ed514c6033","tid":2097090,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"dd8234457898d807f2f8b5dd03aaceb90264cfec","tid":2097090,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e352d469e146fa3ea39d1151978467ea607c8f87","tid":2097090,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:44:32.000Z","msg":"有無立法個段？"},{"pid":"6a31fa4b1429d668ea0a29ed055b9511d9380644","tid":2097090,"uid":312579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"唔好侮辱哈利波特<i